description: Try our easy to follow Chicken Baguette Burgers recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Chicken Baguette Burgers Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 baby cos lettuce, trimmed, leaves washed and dried

recipeInstructions.text: Cut bread stick into 4 pieces and slice through the centre.
Cook chicken in a large non-stick fry pan on high heat, keep turning till chicken is a light brown golden colour or cook chicken breast fillets as per packet instructions.
Add bacon to pan and cook for 2 minutes on each side or until cooked to your liking.
Arrange cos leaves on base of bread stick. Top with slices of chicken and bacon. Drizzle with dressing and cover with top of bread stick.
